<HL>
   Justin's Board Voids
   Election Votes After
   Group Protests Bylaw
</HL>
<DATE>
09/10/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7
</SO>
<CO>
   JSTN TLAM
